title: DDFP 650: Calais Campbell & DeMarcus Lawrence
itunes:title: DDFP 650: Calais Campbell & DeMarcus Lawrence
description:
Dave Dameshek is first joined by Jacksonville Jaguars defensive end and Studio 66 Wall of Famer, Calais Campbell (11:12), who kibitz's about the Jags season ending in the AFC title game (21:37), his NFL Draft Day story (12:15) and a funny on-field moment with Brett Favre (18:40). Next, Dallas Cowboys defensive end DeMarcus Lawrence sits down with Shek (26:47) who talks about being franchise tagged (27:53), why Rod Marinelli is so effective with the Cowboys D (42:30) and the differences between Tony Romo and Dak Prescott (47:35).
